Oh, it would be a story of a - of something that had happened in history - it would be something good - say - a Christian you know - Christian ideas - no - a story of which one would normally tell from materialistic point of view. It had 
to be something based on - Christianity. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14629003 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471752\charrsid5840491 But not necessarily the Bible?
