Not necessarily the Bible but it would be based on that because you see the whole upbringing of my father and mother was based on - on - on - on Christian grounds, you
 see. There was nothing else - accepted - except - law was - law and justice was one thing you see, it was based on Christianity but then they never understood that law was a separate thing - a completely separate thing. Because what was done under the la
w was - was such a damnable lie. There's no truth in it.
