\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247875 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471752\charrsid5840491 Yes. And there came a time when he didn't read at all. But he'd
 have been quite capable had he had spectacles, but you see - then you see when I'm speaking of my family I'm speaking now - it applied generally through the village. I think so much that I've said to you now in regard to family was typical - of the - of 
