\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14629003 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471752\charrsid5840491 Did you wear special clothes for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247875 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471752\charrsid5840491 No. Oh no. I remember - of course I remember the funeral of my b
rother, Fred. That's - 'cos I was in the Army then and I happened to be home on leave when he died. And - 'course he - as I told you - he slept out in a hut outside and - he was - he seemed - seen him maybe as yesterday. He said, you'll be all right, don'
t worry Bill. That'll be all right Fred, you'll be all right too.
