\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247875 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid677048\charrsid5840491 No, I'd get a ha'penny then perhaps but I wouldn't - worry mother about that.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471752\charrsid5840491 
