\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247875 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471752\charrsid5840491 Yes, first time of going, yes. Went back the other way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14629003 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471752\charrsid5840491 Did your elder brothers go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247875 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471752\charrsid5840491 They went to church, yes. Yes.
