 to live with granny. I went to Freeland and of course went to Sunday school. And Sunday school was quite reasonable there for about half an hour and then with the clergyman started going out oh his lawn and then we was down on his lawn and we a
ll spread out and he'd scramble sweets. Yes, he would do that.
