s moist in paper packets you know at that time. And he'd just put it there, resume his work you know and - eventually perhaps on a quiet moment if he wasn't looking I'd just shift it somewhere else. Well he - he'd spot that pretty quickly - realize that i
t was not where he put it in the first instance. And even with regard to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid677048\charrsid5840491 a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9194455\charrsid5840491 squ}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
