rk when he was coming away from his work and - told him all about our troubles. And eventually fixed up with the - another }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12665509\charrsid5840491 man}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471752\charrsid5840491 
 on the - on the estate - we cut this big hedge, yes, that was true.
