 I could shift away to the drum. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12665509\charrsid5840491 I was very embarrassed about that because I was very, very weak. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471752\charrsid5840491 
